812
01:26:36,590 --> 01:26:39,159
Kenapa? Apa ada masalah?

813
01:26:39,159 --> 01:26:40,961
Sebaiknya aku bicara
dengan Tuan Randall.

814
01:26:41,962 --> 01:26:43,864
Dia sedang mandi.

815
01:26:43,864 --> 01:26:45,999
Boleh aku tunggu di dalam?

816
01:26:58,845 --> 01:27:00,414
