untuk memberi pernyataan.

1120
01:59:28,827 --> 01:59:30,428
Dengan senang hati.

1121
01:59:40,338 --> 01:59:43,208
Bisa kuambilkan minuman, Detektif?

1122
01:59:45,143 --> 01:59:46,912
Vodka tonic lagi?

1123
01:59:46,912 --> 01:59:48,346
