1124
01:59:49,548 --> 01:59:51,216
Tak perlu, terima kasih.

1125
01:59:52,484 --> 01:59:54,319
Beri tahu aku
jika kau berubah pikiran.

1126
01:59:55,754 --> 01:59:58,223
